  "title": "A man reported a close encounter with a UFO in Ceilândia-DF [1989]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/10/a-man-reported-a-close-encounter-with-a-ufo-in-ceilandia-df-1989/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1C7",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Ceilândia, Distrito Federal. Date: <strong>March 27th, 1989. Time: 10:30 pm. Duration: 5 minutes.</strong> A Security Agent of the Brasilia Airport spotted an unidentified flying object in the shape of a &#8220;full moon, without emitting strong lights&#8221;. According to the witness, the UFO was small, orange in color and remained stationary between 30 and 50 meters above the observer. Also according to the witness&#8217;s report, &#8220;the object made a 90° turn, however without moving much horizontally&#8221;. The sighting was carried out in a clear sky.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.270. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objetos voadores não identificados um deles sobre Salvador, Estado da Bahia</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>Ceilândia, Distrito Federal. Date: March 27th, 1989. Time: 10:30 pm. Duration: 5 minutes. A Security Agent of the Brasilia Airport spotted an unidentified flying object in the shape of a &#8220;full moon, without emitting strong lights&#8221;. According to the witness, the UFO was small, orange in color and remained stationary between 30 and 50 meters [&hellip;]</p>\n",
